create the env:
python3 -m venv .venv
.venv/bin/pip install fastapi uvicorn pydantic

to run it:
.venv/bin/python fastapi_example.py

.venv/bin/uvicorn fastapi_example:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000 --reload


fastapi_example:app → the file fastapi_example.py, app object inside it
--reload → auto-restarts when you edit code (handy for development; drop it in production)
Then open in your browser:

Swagger UI → http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
ReDoc → http://127.0.0.1:8000/redoc
OpenAPI schema → http://127.0.0.1:8000/openapi.json



